SUMMARY:Baby Animal Tours at Triskelee Farm
DESCRIPTION:Go enjoy a fun-filled day meeting and interacting with adorable farm animals! Get up close and personal with goats\, alpacas\, ostrich chicks\, and more! This is a great opportunity for animal lovers of all ages to learn about these sweet creatures and maybe even make some new furry friends. \nThey provide a fun\, guided educational farm tour. Learn about what and why they farm! Tours will go in with many of our animals to pet and or feed them. \nAdults can take a beverage from the bar along and upgrade to a tipsy tour! They have local beer and wine on tap. \nAfter the tour\, you can hang out on the lawn and purchase food from our food truck. Sourced from the farm. Making it the ultimate farm-to-table experience. \nMore Info\nAdults and children need a ticket. Carried infants are free. \nTours are at 10am and 1pm\nTours last about 40 minutes and will be open to 40 people at a time.\nFood (burgers) and drink (non-alcoholic and alcoholic) will be available for purchase. \nActivities go rain or shine. Expect dirt\, animal droppings\, and uneven slippery surfaces. Please bring or wear closed-toed shoes that you don’t mind getting dirty.
URL:https://pdxparent.com/event-single/baby-animal-tours-as-triskelee-farm/2026-03-21/
LOCATION:Triskelee Farms\, 29700 SW Mountain Rd.\, West Linn\, Oregon\, 97068
CATEGORIES:Active,Animals,Educational,Family Fun,Farm,Kids Calendar,Outdoor
ATTACH;FMTTYPE=image/png:https://pdxparent.com/wp-content/uploads/Baby-Goat-Tours-2.png
GEO:45.305248;-122.690345
