SUMMARY:Big\, Blue Block Play @ SWPMA PLAY!
DESCRIPTION:Join longtime educator/state-certified teacher and movement arts instructor Lara Jones and Wally Jones in the padded play space of SWPMA PLAY! at 5315 SW Capitol Highway in Hillsdale Town Center\, for a Saturday play session for littles ages 0-4. This monthly meetup involves pulling out a large collection of [ImaginationPlayground] blue\, foam play museum blocks…and working cooperatively to build with these oversized blocks! Ramps\, cars & balls are also featured\, and separate areas provided for littles vs walkers. \nThis is a calm\, clean and welcoming space\, where people (largely ignore their phones) take the time to connect with others\, and help facilitate social interactions between their children. \n*Please pre-register and pay here* @ sliding-scale donation\, starting at $1. Pay on site via cash/check is also a choice. Please just write to let us know who to expect info@southwestportlandmartialarts.com: https://southwestportlandmartialarts.com/events/swpma-play/
URL:https://pdxparent.com/event-single/big-blue-block-play-swpma-play-2-2/2026-03-21/
LOCATION:SWPMA PLAY!\, 6315 SW Capitol Highway\, Portland\, 97239\, United States
CATEGORIES:Active,Family Fun,Indoor Play Park,Kids Calendar
