SUMMARY:Tree Time! Preschool Walks
DESCRIPTION:Join us for a story and guided walk on the trails at Hoyt Arboretum. \nWe will use all of our senses to explore the natural surroundings and maybe even get our hands dirty! Staff and trained Arboretum volunteers will introduce you and your family to the plants\, trees\, insects\, mushrooms\, and more found at Hoyt Arboretum. Every Tree Time! walk is a unique\, seasonal\, nature-inspired experience. \nTree Time! walks are held Mondays and Saturdays at 10am year-round. Pre-registration for specific dates is required. \nAges 2-6\, accompanied by a guardian.
URL:https://pdxparent.com/event-single/tree-time-preschool-walks/2026-03-21/
LOCATION:Hoyt Arboretum\, 4000 SW Fairview Blvd\, Portland\, OR\, 97221
CATEGORIES:Educational,Kids Calendar,Outdoor,Plants & Nature,STEM,Storytime
