SUMMARY:Lucky Little Learners
DESCRIPTION:🍀 Lucky Little Learners: A Spring Shamrock Celebration 🌈\nSaturday\, 3/21 | Little Nestlings \nJoin us for a joyful\, hands-on celebration of all things green! This playful morning blends storytelling\, creativity\, exploration\, and a taste of Irish tradition — perfect for welcoming spring together. \n📖 Storytime MagicWe’ll begin with a festive St. Patrick’s Day story to spark imagination and set the tone for a morning of wonder. \n🎨 Green Art StudioChildren will explore a variety of open-ended materials in beautiful shades of green — painting\, collage\, and loose parts — creating their own unique masterpieces inspired by nature and the season. \n🍀 Shamrock Treasure HuntLittle explorers will search high and low for hidden shamrocks throughout our space\, building observation skills and sharing in the excitement of discovery. \n🥖 A Taste of TraditionFamilies can sample bite-sized pieces of traditional Irish brown bread — a simple\, hearty treat to round out the morning. \nThis free community event is open to all families. Come celebrate\, create\, and welcome spring with us! 🍀
URL:https://pdxparent.com/event-single/lucky-little-learners/
LOCATION:Little Nestlings Early Learning Center\, 19200 Willamette Drive\, West Linn\, O\, 97068\, United States
CATEGORIES:Arts/Crafts,Family Fun,Kids Calendar,St. Patrick's,Storytime
