SUMMARY:Kids Workshops at Lowes
DESCRIPTION:Take your mini-builder to Lowes for a morning of constructing! Register ahead of time to reserve a spot. Each workshop lasts about 30 – 45 minutes\, depending on the age of the child and the complexity of that month’s kit. Workshops are generally recommended for kids ages 4 through 11 with parent or guardian supervision. \nWorkshop schedule:\nWashing Machine Bank\nIn store: 1/17/26 from 10 a.m. – 1 p.m. \nBirdhouse\nIn store: 2/21/26 from 10 a.m. – 1 p.m. \nLawn Mower\nIn store: 3/21/26 from 10 a.m. – 1 p.m. \nTerrarium\nIn store: 4/18/26 from 10 a.m. – 1 p.m. \nGarden Basket\nIn store: 5/16/26 from 10 a.m. – 1 p.m. \nTrophy Cup\nIn store: 6/13/26 from 10 a.m. – 1 p.m. \nMini Toy Box\nIn store: 7/11/26 from 10 a.m. – 1 p.m.
URL:https://pdxparent.com/event-single/kids-workshops-at-lowes/2026-03-21/
